Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.21,0:00:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, it'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.75,0:00:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.88,0:00:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.14,0:00:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Kokubu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I’m really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I feel better now, so—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, stay right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Mr. Kokubu,\NI was being quite rude earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, you have nothing at all to be sorry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we talk about what to do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Small Palm
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey, Mr. Kokubu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}How long are you\Ngoing to keep calling me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}didn't I already apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. With your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry for what I did.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I apologized and I'm keeping\Nmy mouth shut in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Part of the work\Nis becoming aware of what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen if I become aware of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will something change?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If something changes,\Nwill I get something good out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Mr. Kokubu,\Nwill something good happen if we keep living?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My parents and everyone around me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,say do your best and study hard\Nso you can get into a good high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but even if I got into a good school,\Nwho's to say I'll get a job at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,let alone one at a good company?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"If you do your best, you'll get good results,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no guarantee of that,\Nand still people say, "Do your best!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like, if I worked as hard as I could,\Nbut it didn't work out,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,nobody's going to take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're nervous about the future\Nbecause of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And your parents don't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What part of that has anything to do\Nwith Kawamoto and Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely nothing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Stop talking like you've come to the conclusion\Nthat it's all society's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Keep it up and I'll start talking about life\Nin Japan when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The postwar period!\NIt was still postwar times!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}If I did that, you'd be like,\N"That has nothing to do with this." Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't understand how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm asking now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. The perilla plant is set.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We can put the basil next to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And let's put the mint somewhere else.\NIt grows too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.57,0:05:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's give them plenty of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Last week in homeroom, Mr. Kokubu said\Nsomething to the class with a clear voice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, today there are several things\NI want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}First, Arai, Takashi, Kimura,\NMochizuki, Takagi, and Wakabayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are individual questions for you six,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so you'll each go with a teacher\Nto another classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's when everyone in the class realized.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The school had gotten serious\Nabout intervening in the darkness in our class.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now we knew this teacher wasn't just\Ngoing through the motions of doing something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll get started here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what's really going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unwritten rules that had spread in our class{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}wouldn't work anymore from now on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone realized that\Nmaybe the days of living in fear{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}of becoming the next target may now be over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, the curtain came down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm sorry.\N- I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With words that made it hard to tell\Nif it was really over at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't one bit of sincerity in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we've still got a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kokubu, is it okay if I don't forgive them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just, "apologize and you'll be forgiven,"\Nwith no punishment given.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about\Nhow Chiho had to change schools...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's too much to forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Compassion"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I'm kind of drawing a blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that like "hypocrisy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like something you need, or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Education" huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If only it were as easy as it sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our job is to "teach" and "raise" students.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take "raise" out of the equation,\Nand I would never have gotten involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in this whole issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Snore snore...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:08:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wheeze...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS. HINATA KAWAMOTO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FROM CHIHO SAKURA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Chiho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hina, I'm sorry it's taken me so long\Nto get back to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Right now, I'm studying with a teacher\Nin a place called a "Heart Care Center."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a quiet, pretty area\Nsurrounded by mountains and forests.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's a ranch and farm next to the center.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:10:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They let me help out there sometimes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a baby goat that was born on the ranch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her name is Mei.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dog to my left is Hana.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They always come running over\Nto see me when I go to the ranch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're the first friends I made here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}All of the people on the farm and ranch\Nare very friendly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}The people in the neighborhood, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}The other day, we made plum wine,\Nplum syrup, and plum jam together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My mom helped too,\Nand we had a good time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:11:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My dad's office isn't too far from the center,\Nso he drops me off and picks me up every day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm really happy to have more chances\Nto talk to him now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I first came here, I couldn't get used to\Nthis new place, so I was really lonely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But then Ms. Satou, my teacher at the center,\Ntaught me the "three steps to making a friend."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You start by making friends with animals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After you do that, the next step is making friends\Nwith people who are older than you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:11:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And today...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TO MS. SATOU
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ms. Satou said,\N"Why don't we move on to the third step?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The third step is making friends with someone\Nwho's close to your own age.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I heard that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought about you, Hina.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really miss you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the plum syrup is just right,\NI'd like to drink some with you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I planted corn too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be ready to pick by August.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd like to eat the corn with you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will you come and visit me\Nduring summer vacation?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can I look forward to seeing you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From Chiho{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Small Palm
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}In the Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}TSUKUDAKO BRIDGE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's sleeping.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Wants to go in, but can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unsure if it's okay to enter\Na house where a girl's sleeping
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ooph...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Sat down for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I wonder why.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}For the first time in a while,\Nit's like she has a soft aura around her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Like she's faintly glowing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Feels like I could look at her like this forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rei.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}Apparently nodded off
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Summer tangerines!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:16:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My workshop mentor gave them to me.\NHe picked a ton, so told me to take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe I fell asleep on her doorstep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So many...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Mr. Shimada?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It grew on your property,\Nbut you won't eat any?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I have a feeling the acid in the tangerines\Nwould melt through my stomach lining.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are no pesticides on them,\Nso you can make jam and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}HAHAHA...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jam?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}JAM?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}OH
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're saving me money on groceries again!\NI'll make jam!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be great.\NSis's marmalade is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as I thought, she's faintly glowing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder why.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It seems like it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I think it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see. That must be why...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she's glowing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cute, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We baked them yesterday\Nat my classmate Kawashima's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We're in the same group.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:18:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was me, Kawashima, Kiuchi,\NKobayashi and Kudou, so five of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kawamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we're going to make cookies today\Nat Kawashima's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Want to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.19,0:18:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we apologize, we thought that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you might not forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I really wanted to apologize to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that, I changed clothes,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.51,0:18:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then met up with the girls\Nat Kawashima's house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We baked a lot of cookies together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The cookies turned out hard and misshapen...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? It's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After I said that, we couldn't stop laughing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While we were laughing, we said,\N"Still, cookies right out of the oven are good,"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and we kept on eating them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder why.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Store-bought cookies taste much better,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I had such a good time\Nand was so happy that they were delicious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you put a cookie fresh from the oven\Nto your mouth, it sizzles?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I burned the inside of my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saying that, she innocently\Nopened her mouth wide.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I saw the sunlight\Non her teeth and tongue,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.03,0:20:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}for some reason\Nvarious feelings welled up inside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had a tightening sensation in my chest\Nand felt like I was going to cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. Even though I promised right here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that I would protect you that day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.61,0:21:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you listened...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all those times?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you went to Kyoto\Nto search for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you made me so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I wasn't able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:21:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me, "After all!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.73,0:21:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}EHHH
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No buts!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, you're an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}CHOMP
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right! Guess what!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I got a letter from Chiho!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.12,0:22:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From Chiho? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.08,0:22:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then, and then!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.29,0:22:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,During summer vacation,\NI'm going to visit her, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.13,0:22:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While telling me that, she pulled me\Nby the hand as if we were dancing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.64,0:22:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and started walking at a steady pace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.14,0:22:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And to this small heroine who never gave in,\Nno matter how much she cried or suffered,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.28,0:22:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I made another promise,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,0:22:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}and a little oath of loyalty in my head.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:23:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:36.77,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 36
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.68,0:24:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?\NWhat is this poster?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.35,0:24:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The design is really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.68,0:24:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.43,0:24:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.35,0:24:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But for some reason,\Nit doesn't feel real.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.15,0:24:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you tell her that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.65,0:24:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.65,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because you've been listening\Nto her all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.03,0:24:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}ILLUSTRATION:\NAKIO WATANABE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.03,0:24:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll have Sis tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.99,0:24:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,how to make marmalade\Nso I can make it, too!
